---
name: Onboard Check Point structured-data syslog via UDP
description: |
  Reads Check Point structured-data syslog over UDP, extracts the exported
  Check Point fields, and publishes normalized records to the topic
  `checkpoint`.
disabled: true
restart-on-error: 1m
---

accept_udp "{{ inputs.syslog-url }}"
this = {...data.parse_syslog(), raw: data}
checkpoint::syslog::parse_structured_data
publish "checkpoint"
